description:
Today on the show we flashed back to our interview with Donnell Rawlings, so you know there was some trolling and jokes popping off through out the interview. Moreover, for Freaky Friday they flashed back to when we had the host of the Whoreible Decisions Podcast Mandii B and Weezy who schooled Breakfast Club on pegging, being sexually free and more.
